hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.title: Hoe Tweaks Config
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_onlyUnt: When enabled, only allows the un-till function to work when the other hand is empty. Allows placing seeds with hoe in other hand.
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.onlyUntillWi: Only Untill With Other Hand Empty
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_cropBlo: How much quicker a cropblock (pumpkin/melon) is broken than by default.
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_mustCro: Whether the bigger hoe range should only be used if the player is crouching when right-clicking the center block.
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.mustCrouchTo: Must Crouch To Have Bigger Hoe Range
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_woodenT: The wooden hoe till range (default while crouching). 0 = 1x1
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_stoneTi: The wooden hoe till range (default while crouching). 1 = 3x3
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_goldTie: The wooden hoe till range (default while crouching). 2 = 5x5
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_ironTie: The wooden hoe till range (default while crouching). 2 = 5x5
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_diamond: The wooden hoe till range (default while crouching). 3 = 7x7
hoetweaks-fabric.duskconfig.DESC_netheri: The wooden hoe till range (default while crouching). 4 = 9x9
